Draw compose
============

Render compose files with one command line!

This project needs graphviz installed.

Simple example
--------------

.. figure:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Alexis-benoist/draw-compose/master/fixtures/simple.png?raw=true
   :alt: Simple Example

   Simple example

